<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2024-01 on</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024-01/</link><description>Recent content in 2024-01 on</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024-01/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>완전한날</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog19/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog19/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="완전한날"&gt;
 완전한날
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%99%84%ec%a0%84%ed%95%9c%eb%82%a0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-25&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f0c23bb1-f520-4312-a4b8-c50653c59c45" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;내가 행복하면 남들은 눈에들어오지않는다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로산 틴트가 마음에 들구 새로산 가디건두 맘에 든다 ㅎ 하나 더 살까 고민중.
오늘 얼굴상태도 맘에든다. 옷도 괜찮다. 공부도 맘에 든다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/febd2e92-41cb-4a3d-a20a-1d9cea3ee3a0" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;운동도 하고 집에 왔다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;집와서 블루베리랑 귤이랑 사과랑 자유시간이랑 초콜릿남은거 먹었다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>완전한날</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog18/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog18/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="완전한날"&gt;
 완전한날
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%99%84%ec%a0%84%ed%95%9c%eb%82%a0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2024-01-15&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘은 운동도 하고 공부는 조금만했지만 괜찮고 말실수도 안했고. 엄마한테 기분좋은일도 안겨주었고 화목 7시부터 8시까지하는 요가수업도 신청했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;식단을 지키고 엄마와 거리를 유지하면서 주변사람을 잘챙기고, 돈을 적당히 쓰고, 사람에게 화내지않고, 말을 많이 하지말고 잘 졸업하자&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1179" height="1263" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f4afcbd4-8e1f-4a41-8413-53e314bc4986" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="459" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c144cbdc-1a29-4d76-aa61-87e3219ca54c" /&gt;</description></item><item><title>생일생일</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2024/24blog1/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="생일생일"&gt;
